Sas kaucuk

SAS KAUCUK

20 yllk otomotiv ana sanayi tecrbesi nda  otomotiv yedek para sektrnden balayarak, otomotiv sektrne hizmet etmek amacyla 1990 ylnda kurulmutur.

Son teknolojik tasarm, retim ve test olanaklarn kullanarak kendi mhendislik, ar-ge ve retim tesislerinde otomotiv yan sanayi ve yedek para sektrne rnler retmektedir.

Kauuk, metal ve alminyum younluklu para guruplarnda amortisr takozlar, motor takozlar, burlar, krkler gibi metal- aluminyum - kauuk aksaml  paralarn retimlerine odaklanmaktadr.

SAS KAUCUKun ynetim anlayna, kaliteli retim, rekabeti fiyat ve zamannda teslim gibi n koullar dikkate alnarak, sat sonras tam destek prensibiyle, koulsuz tketici memnuniyetinin salanmas gibi temel ilkeler yn vermektedir.

Mhendislik yeteneklerini kullanarak, orijinal yedek para kalitesinde rnler reterek sektrnde lider retici olmay, salad tm imkanlar ve sat politikalaryla otomotiv yedek para toptanclar iin en uygun partner olmay  hedeflemektedir.

item.title: CORPORATE
item.dc:creator: tylerhuso
item.content:encoded:
Sas Kaucuk is founded in 1990 in order to supply automobile spare parts with 30 years automotive main industry experience. Sas Kaucuk provide spare parts using high technology design tools with its own rnd department and using its own facility. We focus on spare parts based on rubber, metal, aluminium such as damper mount, engine mounts, bearing, bellows.

SAS KAUCUK managing approach based on high quality production, competitive price, delivery on time, consideration after-sale service demands and customer satisfaction. Our purpose is to be leader of the market, best solution for spare parts suppliers using our engineering abilities and experiences.
